name: IBS
public_notice: 24th Oct 2022 - IBS had recently migrated from their TRON (TRC-20) contract to a BSC (BEP-20) contract , kindly refer to this post for more information.

description.en: IBS is the utility token of "International Blockchain Service and Academy" ( IBSA PVT LTD.). IBS token is required for all products and services offered by IBSA . IBS is targeting the Blockchain service and Crypto education market of India and other developing countries like Bangladesh, Pakistan, and Sri Lanka, Nepal , Bhutan etc.
